<header class="header">
  <h1>Best Seed Company for Succession Planting</h1>
  <p class="tagline">
    Succession planting works when timing is clear and crops are reliable.
  </p>
  <p class="lede">
    <strong>For most gardeners, Johnny’s Selected Seeds is the best seed company for succession planting because it makes maturity timing easy to compare across crops. High Mowing Organic Seeds is a strong alternative for consistent performance across repeated plantings, and West Coast Seeds works well in cooler or shorter seasons.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    Succession planting is less about planting more and more about planting at the right intervals. That depends on choosing crops that mature predictably and fit into your available window.
  </p>
  <p>
    The best seed companies make those decisions easier.
  </p>
</header>

<section class="guideSection">
  <h2>Quick Picks: Best Seed Companies for Succession Planting</h2>

  <div class="quickAnswerBox">
